comments: Towns (MIN) contests Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt and marginal hand to hand contact occurs after Jokic's (DEN) follow through.
Jokic (DEN) establishes his defensive position in Edwards' (MIN) path and absorbs the side to side contact on Edwards' driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) does not put part of his hand under the ball, and either carry it from one point to another or bring it to a pause and then continue to dribble again.
Towns (MIN) extends both arms forward and initiates body contact with Jokic (DEN) that affects his SQBR in the post.
Murray (DEN) slightly steps towards Towns (MIN) and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Gobert (MIN) firms up his defensive position in Jokic's (DEN) path and absorbs the oncoming contact on his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) brings his forearm to Gobert's (MIN) body and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to retrieve the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) extends his forearm to his left and delivers contact to Gobert's (MIN) arm/side and affects his ability to rebound.
Towns (MIN) is drawn into the air and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) body which affects his shot near the rim.
Gobert (MIN) reaches in and initiates contact with Brown's (DEN) arm that affects his SQBR.
Conley (MIN) reaches in and initiates contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Brown (DEN) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Brown (DEN) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Edwards' (MIN) arm.
